replies.body:
An all AD team is vulnerable to very high armor builds. Similarly, an all AP team is vulnerable to high MR builds. Take, for example, this build:

{{item:3102}} {{item:3065}} {{item:3190}} {{item:3111}} {{item:3512}} {{item:3083}} 

An all AP team will have a lot of trouble breaking down the tank, so a skilled tank can keep their team alive for far longer than if there was an AD champion there. The same applies for a build like

{{item:3025}} {{item:3047}} {{item:3742}} {{item:3110}} {{item:3143}} {{item:3083}} 

which an AD champion will have a lot of trouble with. Obviously this can be mitigated with penetration stats, but it is much harder than to just have a mixed damage team.
